  • Classes in com.telenav.kivakit.core.commandline used by com.telenav.kivakit.core.application 
    Class Description
    ApplicationMetadata
    Application metadata used in formulating command line usage help.
    ArgumentList
    A list of Arguments passed on a command line and retrieved with CommandLine.arguments() after command line parsing with CommandLineParser.
    ArgumentParser
    Parses a command-line Argument, as defined by a Quantifier, a type, a string converter for that type and a human-readable description.
    CommandLine
    A parsed command line of switches and (non-switch) arguments.
    SwitchParser
    A switch parser that can be passed to CommandLine.get(SwitchParser) to retrieve a switch value.

    CommandLine
    A parsed command line of switches and (non-switch) arguments.
    CommandLineParser
    Parses an array of command line arguments into a list of SwitchList of the form "-switch=value" and a list of remaining non-switch arguments in an ArgumentList.
    Quantifier
    Specifies the number of arguments required or allowed
    Switch
    Represents a switch argument, with a name and value.
